196
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:09,386
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga! Anda sudah datang.</font>

197
00:19:09,386 --> 00:19:10,653
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda datang jauh-jauh kesini.</font>

198
00:19:12,144 --> 00:19:13,553
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda siapa?</font>

199
00:19:13,553 --> 00:19:15,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku direktur Hospice
