201
00:19:18,529 --> 00:19:20,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, Anda direkturnya disini?</font>

202
00:19:20,950 --> 00:19:23,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat menghormati
orang seperti Anda.</font>

203
00:19:25,009 --> 00:19:28,162
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena Anda di sini, mari
