208
00:19:38,789 --> 00:19:40,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau lihat? Dia ada di sini
bukan untuk kegiatan amal.</font>

209
00:19:40,519 --> 00:19:41,721
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami mencintaimu!</font>

210
00:19:43,367 --> 00:19:44,744
<font color=#FFFF00>Cukup bagus, 'kan?</font>

211
00:19:44,744 --> 00:19:48,073
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bisa membangun hotel di sini.
Dengan cara ini...</font>

212
00:19:52,565 --> 00:19:55,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini akan naik
ke sini seperti ini.</font>

213
00:20:01,099 --> 00:20:02,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa, Bibi?</font>

214
00:20:04,958 --> 00:20:07,078
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan Shi Kyung?
